Hi, my name is Alexander.
I am a web-developer. My preferences are part of knowledge in a lot of technologies and deep knowledge in some of them.
When I am working on a project I like to speak with client, to clear understanding what client needs and then to implement the project.

My skills and experience are:
— PHP/OOP
